{
  "stem": "232.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, we went to Tel Aviv, and I lived with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother was living in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She took us in, my brother and me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother was still in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I was on the transport to Palestine, my father was still in Italy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when he heard that I go to Palestine, he took a taxi from Rome with-- with-- with a friend's father whose son was with me on the-- on the boat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted to-- he came to Napoli by taxi to take us off the boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He want us-- he did not want us to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they-- they missed the boat-- like you said, they missed the boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They saw the smoke, the boat leaving Napoli, when-- when they arrived there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my-- my father decided that they will come too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They joined us and-- my father joined in 1945, later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my mother, too, joined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She came-- believe it or not, she came with the children transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was smuggled from-- with the children transport to Haifa from France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother, my father, my brother, and I, we were together, all together in Israel-- in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister was in America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she-- she went to America because she thought that everybody was killed, was-- she knew only we were deported.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't know that my brother and father escaped, and my mother was taken for dead anyway a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the [INAUDIBLE] invited a boat of 900 refugees, a gesture in 1990-- in 1944, and my sister-- my sister was on this boat, was-- was taken to Fort Ontario.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
